name: XMP || Mona Card || (2018)
description:
XMP on MONACARD. This card is similar currency to PEPECASH on Counterparty. 

Issuer: Nobody(発行者なし); 
Description: Monapartyトークンを発行するときに手数料として必要なトークンです。

This is a wrapped Monaparty asset. The MONA seed phrase is embedded in the vault. 
Original Card issued on Monaparty. Launched in Jan. 2018. The shortest and most appropriate explanation of Monaparty is "a token platform based on Counterparty". Its design and function are inherited from the original Counterparty of Bitcoin. However, some Monaparty original features were added, and the base chain was changed to Monacoin.



View contents of NFT by expanding Properties Below and at Emblem.Finance 👇

[View this NFT on Emblem.Finance](https://emblem.finance/nft?id=57085426745316461)

XMP Explorer: [MJQ4FtcsUvfF1p4XteXxEZ3jYuF3VMQbaX](https://card.mona.jp/explorer/address_detail?address=MJQ4FtcsUvfF1p4XteXxEZ3jYuF3VMQbaX)
